      "content": "English: Gerizim - French: Garizim - Latin: Garizim - Origin: &#1490;&#1468;&#1456;&#1512;&#1460;&#1494;&#1460;&#1497;&#1501; - Vietnamese: Gơ-ri-dim Gs 8,30-33 ; Tl 9,7",
